TruckNav Pro Terms of Service - Plain Language Version
Last Updated: January 2025
The Short Version
Use the app legally and safely. Don't use it while driving. We're a tool to help you, but you're still responsible for following the rules of the road and DOT regulations.
What TruckNav Pro Does
GPS navigation made for big trucks
Hours of Service (HOS) tracking
Expense tracking and tax help
Trip planning and route optimization
Find truck stops and weigh stations
Traffic and weather updates
Who Can Use This App
You must be 18 or older
You should have a valid CDL (if you're driving commercially)
You must follow all trucking laws
You must be able to legally agree to these terms
Your Account
Creating one:
Sign up with email/password or Apple Sign In
Give us accurate info
Keep your password secret
You're responsible for everything that happens on your account
Deleting it:
You can delete anytime in Settings
We can delete your account if you break these rules
No refunds if we kick you out
Pricing & Payment
Plan	Price	Free Trial
Monthly	$12.99/month	7 days
Yearly	$99/year	7 days
