How it works:
Free trial = 7 days, no charge
Cancel anytime during trial = no charge
After trial, you get billed automatically
Auto-renews unless you cancel 24 hours before it renews
Cancel in iOS Settings → Subscriptions
Refunds:
All sales are final
Apple handles refunds, not us
Contact Apple Support if you want a refund
Safety Rules (Important!)
⚠️ WARNING:
NEVER use this app while driving
Pull over before touching your phone
A passenger can use the app for you
Use voice navigation for hands-free directions
YOU are responsible for driving safely
Your Responsibilities
Follow the law:
FMCSA regulations
DOT rules
Hours of Service rules
State and local trucking laws
This app helps you, but it doesn't replace your legal obligations. Keep your info accurate:
Enter correct truck specs (height, weight, length, hazmat)
Update when things change
Double-check routes before you drive
You're ultimately responsible for choosing safe routes
About HOS logging:
Our HOS tracking is for your convenience
It's NOT a certified ELD (Electronic Logging Device)
If you need a real ELD, use one - don't rely only on us
Make sure your logs are accurate
Don't Do This
Use the app for anything illegal
Break trucking laws
Hack, modify, or reverse-engineer the app
Share your account
Lie about your info
Mess with other users
Try to break into our systems
If you do these things, we'll terminate your account and might take legal action.
